title: SCP-2001-EX Fragment 2
content:

You are still reading this. [[span style="color:white"]]You're in the wrong iteration.[[/span]]
SCP-2001 Exempt Personnel do not exist. [[span style="color:white"]]Not anymore, at least.[[/span]]
Please remain in your seat. Site security has been dispatched to this workstation.
author: Annabelle Dillard
